### Stack overview

- **Language/Types**: TypeScript (strict)
- **Runtime/PM/Test**: Bun 1.2.x (scripts, `bun test`)
- **Build**: tsup (ESM, dts)
- **Platform/Deploy**: Cloudflare Workers via Wrangler
- **Web/API**: Hono
- **Telegram Bot**: grammY
- **DB/ORM**: Drizzle ORM + Cloudflare D1 (drizzle-kit, `d1-http` driver)
- **AI/Agents**: LangChain JS + LangGraph (OpenAI/Groq/Tavily providers)
- **Solana/Drift**: `@drift-labs/sdk`, `@solana/web3.js`, `@coral-xyz/anchor`, `solana-agent-kit`
- **Auth/Identity**: Privy Server SDK
- **Validation**: Zod
- **Format/Lint**: Biome
- **Observability**: Cloudflare Workers Observability enabled
- **Compat flags**: `nodejs_compat`, `nodejs_compat_populate_process_env`

### Key config files

- `package.json` — scripts, dependencies
- `wrangler.jsonc` — Workers entry (`src/worker.ts`), D1 binding, observability, compat flags
- `drizzle.config.ts` — local SQLite via `LOCAL_DB_PATH` or Cloudflare D1 via `d1-http`
- `tsconfig.json` — strict TS, bundler resolution, `hono/jsx`, `bun` types
- `src/routes/` — Hono routes (e.g., `webhook.ts`)
- `src/db/schema/` — Drizzle schema and migrations source

